      '<p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">Para dar de alta, tenés que comunicarte con <a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="http://misEjecutivos" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">tu Ejecutivo.</span></strong></a> Una vez finalizado el proceso, se comunicaran con vos para darte tu <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">número de convenio</strong> y comentarte los pasos a seguir.</p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">Una vez que ya tengas el alta, vas a poder<strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"> </strong>descargar, completar y enviar los archivos<strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"> por Office Banking</strong> desde <a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="https://wsec06.bancogalicia.com.ar/Cobros/PagoDirecto" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">Cobros &gt; Pago directo↗</span></strong></a></p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph ghq-is-empty" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"></p>',
