    guruId: "9beecad6-8ecf-42c1-a8cc-7c25e20b9d68",
    htmlContent:
      '<h2 class="ghq-card-content__medium-heading" data-ghq-card-content-type="MEDIUM_HEADING"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Por Office Banking</strong></h2><ol class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST" start="1"><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Desde <a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="https://wsec06.bancogalicia.com.ar/PagoDirecto/RecepcionArchivos" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Cobros &gt; Pago directo &gt; Descargar archivos</strong></span><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">↗</span></strong></a></li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Filtrá por fecha &gt; Clic en <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">"Consultar"</strong> y <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">¡listo!</strong></li></ol><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">Lo vas a poder hacer después de las <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">72 horas</strong> hábiles del vencimiento de las facturas.</p><h3 class="ghq-card-content__small-heading" data-ghq-card-content-type="SMALL_HEADING">Existen 3 tipos de archivos:</h3><ul class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST"><li class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST_ITEM"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">ADH-ADH:</strong> notifica a la empresa sobre las novedades, como el pedido de altas, bajas o modificaciones.</li><li class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST_ITEM"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">COB-COB:</strong> detalla el estado de cada cobro por cliente. Indica los débitos que se hicieron y los que se rechazaron.</li><li class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST_ITEM"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">REV-REV: </strong>informa las reversiones procesadas.</li></ul><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph ghq-is-empty" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"></p>',
