    htmlContent:
      '<p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">Para modificar las condiciones, tenés que seguir estos pasos:</p><ol class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST" start="1"><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Solicitar a<strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60"> </span></strong><a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="http://misEjecutivos" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">tu </span></strong><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Ejecutivo</strong></span></a> el formulario <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">"F5137-3 Solicitud de Servicio de Pago Directo"</strong> &gt; Marcar la opción Modificar.</li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Seleccionar los cambios que querés realizar &gt; Firmar.</li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Subilo <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">por Office Banking</strong> desde: <a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="https://wsec06.bancogalicia.com.ar/Users/SpecialWelcome" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">Cobros &gt; Pago directo &gt;Envío de archivo</span></strong><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">↗</span></strong></a> y <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">¡listo!</strong></li></ol><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">☝️ Recibirás una notificación cuando se aplique el cambio.</p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph ghq-is-empty" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"></p>',
