    guruId: "f8089076-c27a-49f3-bb87-7a34e96e0b19",
    htmlContent:
      '<h2 class="ghq-card-content__medium-heading" data-ghq-card-content-type="MEDIUM_HEADING"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Por Office Banking</strong></h2><ol class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST" start="1"><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Ingresá con el rol de administrador &gt; Administrar Empresa &gt; Permisos de usuarios &gt; Seleccioná en modo de asignación <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">"Por funcionalidad"</strong>.</li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Elegí el usuario &gt; Hacé clic en "Continuar".</li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Dentro de la sección Cobros &gt; Consultar &gt; Tildá las funcionalidades que necesites &gt; Habilitá el perfil de Cobranza Integrada y <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">¡listo!</strong></li></ol><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph ghq-is-empty" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"><a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="http:///n4/como-descargo-y-envio-el-registro-de-cobranza-integrada" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">Conocé cómo descargar y enviar tu registro de Cobranza Integrada.</span></strong></a></p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph ghq-is-empty" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"></p>',
