    guruId: "0c9644c2-8007-4e6c-b942-c58c47e28a4c",
    htmlContent:
      '<p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">Podés enviar y recibir información sobre tus cobros desde:</p><ul class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST"><li class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST_ITEM"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Office Banking:</strong> subís y descargás tus archivos en formato .TXT o .ZIP.</li><li class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST_ITEM"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">SFTP:</strong> te conectás a un directorio del Banco para enviar y recibir archivos encriptados (para usar este canal tenés que contactar a tu Ejecutivo/a).</li><li class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST_ITEM"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">API de Cobros:</strong> podés intercambiar información de tus cobranzas con Galicia de forma online, en cualquier momento y siempre que sea necesario (para usar este canal tenés que contactar a <a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="http://misEjecutivos" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">tu Ejecutivo/a</span></strong></a>).</li></ul><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">Conocé cómo funciona Cobranza Integrada</span></strong></p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph ghq-is-empty" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"></p>',
