    htmlContent:
      '<h2 class="ghq-card-content__medium-heading" data-ghq-card-content-type="MEDIUM_HEADING"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Por Office Banking</strong></h2><ol class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST" start="1"><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Desde <a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="https://wsec06.bancogalicia.com.ar/DebitoInmediato/AdhesionVendedorPreparar" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Cobros &gt; Cobros DEBIN &gt; Adhesión DEBIN↗</strong></span></a></li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Seleccioná la cuenta que querés adherir &gt; Clic en <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">"Adherir"</strong>.</li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Confirmá &gt; Ingresá el Token y <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">¡listo!</strong></li></ol><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">Si no sabés cómo generar tu Token, <a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="http:///n4/como-activo-mi-office-token" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">seguí estos pasos.</span></strong></a></p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Importante:</strong> en la cuenta que adheriste, también acreditaremos los pagos que te realicen a través de DEBIN.</p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">☝️ Si querés dar de baja la cuenta, tenés que seleccionar el cesto de basura que se encuentra a la izquierda del número de cuenta.</p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph ghq-is-empty" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"></p>',
