    htmlContent:
      '<p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">Si las facturas no aparecen dentro de Office es porque no ingresaron al <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Sistema de Cirulación Abierta (SCA).</strong></p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">Las facturas se transmiten al SCA si se dan dos condiciones: el emisor elige el SCA al emitir la factura en la <a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="https://www.afip.gob.ar/landing/default.asp" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">web de la AFIP</span></strong></a> y el comprador acepta de forma expresa o tácita.</p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph ghq-is-empty" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"></p>',
