    guruId: "7aef3227-01c4-4f98-b5ee-fffd67200121",
    htmlContent:
      '<p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">Podés hacerlo y<strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"> </strong>anticipar la fecha de cobro. Al vender las facturas, se te cobrará una comisión que lo vas a encontrar al finalizar el proceso y se descontará del total de la factura a cobrar.</p><h2 class="ghq-card-content__medium-heading" data-ghq-card-content-type="MEDIUM_HEADING"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Por Office Banking</strong></h2><ol class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST" start="1"><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Ingresá a <a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="https://wsec06.bancogalicia.com.ar/Fce/ini" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">Cuentas &gt; Factura de Crédito Electrónica</span></strong><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">↗</span></strong></a></li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Clic sobre los tres puntos al lado del estado de la factura &gt; Vender y <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">¡listo!</strong></li></ol><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">☝️ <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Importante:</strong> para poder vender tu factura, su estado debe ser <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">"Activa"</strong>.</p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph ghq-is-empty" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"><a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="http:///n4/cuales-son-los-estados-de-facturas-de-credito-electronica" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">Conocé cuales son los estados.</span></strong></a></p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph ghq-is-empty" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"></p>',
