    htmlContent:
      '<h2 class="ghq-card-content__medium-heading" data-ghq-card-content-type="MEDIUM_HEADING"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Limite por orden </strong></h2><ul class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST"><li class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST_ITEM"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Todas las empresas:</strong> hasta $1.000.000</li></ul><h2 class="ghq-card-content__medium-heading" data-ghq-card-content-type="MEDIUM_HEADING"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Limite por día</strong></h2><ul class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST"><li class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST_ITEM"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Negocios y PyME:</strong> hasta $1.000.000</li><li class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST_ITEM"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Resto de empresas:</strong> hasta $2.000.000</li></ul><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">☝️ Siempre y cuando no superes el disponible diario de Office Banking. </p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Importante:</strong> si el CUIT/CUIL que está operando en Office Banking es <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">de una persona física</strong> y no de una empresa, el límite es mas bajo.</p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph ghq-is-empty" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"></p>',
