    htmlContent:
      '<p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">El dinero se extrae solamente de las <a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="https://www.galicia.ar/personas/sucursales" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">terminales de autoservicio</span></strong></a> que tengan la función de retirar efectivo.</p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">Para realizar la extracción se debe ingresar los siguientes datos:</p><ul class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST"><li class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST_ITEM">El DNI del destinatario.</li><li class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST_ITEM">El monto de la operación.</li><li class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST_ITEM">El código de extracción de <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">6 dígitos</strong>.</li></ul><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph ghq-is-empty" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"></p>',
