    htmlContent:
      '<p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">Puede que esté configurado como <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">"privado"</strong> y solo el usuario administrador tiene acceso.</p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">Si sos el <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">administrador</strong>, podés cambiar la configuración del contacto <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">desde Office Banking:</strong></p><ol class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST" start="1"><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Desde <a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="https://wsec06.bancogalicia.com.ar/Administracion/AgendaUsuarioAdministrador" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">Administrar Empresa (menú lateral izquierdo) &gt; Agenda de contactos empresa</span></strong><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">↗</span></strong></a></li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Filtrá por CUIT, CUIL, CDI o por la descripción que hayas elegido &gt; Hacé clic en Consultar.</li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Seleccioná el contacto &gt; En "Tipo de contacto" seleccioná "Público" y <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">¡listo!</strong></li></ol><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">☝️ En caso de que necesites compartir toda la agenda, podés <a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="http:///n4/como-exporto-mis-contactos-a-un-archivo" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">exportarla</span></strong></a> y enviarla a quien quieras.</p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph ghq-is-empty" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"></p>',
