    htmlContent:
      '<h2 class="ghq-card-content__medium-heading" data-ghq-card-content-type="MEDIUM_HEADING"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Por Office Banking</strong></h2><ol class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST" start="1"><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Desde <a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="https://wsec06.bancogalicia.com.ar/Transferencias/NuevaTransferencia/nueva-transferencia" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">Pagos &gt; Transferencia &gt; Nueva transferencia</span></strong><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">↗</strong></span></a></li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">En Datos del destinatario, hacé clic en <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">"Agenda"</strong>.</li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Buscá, seleccioná el contacto que querés  &gt; Clic en <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">"listo"</strong>.</li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Clic en <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">"Continuar"</strong> &gt; Preparar y autorizar.</li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Ingresá tu <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">c</strong><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">ódigo</strong> <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Office Token</strong> que generás desde la App y<strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"> ¡listo!</strong></li></ol><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"><a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="http:///n4/por-que-no-encuentro-un-contacto-en-la-agenda" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">Conocé qué hacer si no encontrás un contacto.</span></strong></a></p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Importante:</strong> las transferencias pueden demorar <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">hasta 24 h</strong>. En caso de estar en estado <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">"En ejecución"</strong> verificar que la cuenta débito tenga saldo o acuerdo suficiente para realizar el descuento total de la transferencia + comisiones e impuestos, en caso contrario pasará a estado<strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"> "Rechazada"</strong> por saldo insuficiente.</p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph ghq-is-empty" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"></p>',
