    parent: "67239e5b832f86e945c02ff0",
    guruId: "92238527-e369-45b0-a117-81aecd196b81",
    htmlContent:
      '<h2 class="ghq-card-content__medium-heading" data-ghq-card-content-type="MEDIUM_HEADING"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Por Office Banking</strong></h2><ol class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST" start="1"><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Desde <a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="https://wsec06.bancogalicia.com.ar/Transaction/ListPendingMultiple" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Autorizar operaciones</strong></span><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">↗</strong></span></a> &gt;<strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"> </strong>Seleccioná la operación a autorizar &gt; Hacé clic en Autorizar.</li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Revisá que el detalle de la transacción esté bien &gt; Autorizar.</li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Ingresá el código <a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="http:///n4/como-genero-el-office-token" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">Office Token</span></strong></a> que generarás desde la App Galicia Office &gt; Continuar y <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">¡listo!</strong></li></ol><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">Tené en cuenta que, una vez autorizada, no podrás cancelarla.</p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">☝️ Podés seleccionar <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">hasta 20</strong> operaciones al mismo tiempo.</p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">Si no tenés Token activo te vamos a pedir autorizar mediante reconocimiento facial, <a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="http:///n4/como-preparo-autorizo-operaciones-reconocimiento-facial" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">conocé como realizarlo.</span></strong></a></p><h2 class="ghq-card-content__medium-heading" data-ghq-card-content-type="MEDIUM_HEADING"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Por App Galicia Office</strong></h2><ol class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST" start="1"><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Desde Autorizar &gt; Pendientes &gt; Ver operaciones.</li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Seleccioná autorizar &gt; Autorizar operación y<strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"> ¡listo!</strong></li></ol><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"><a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="http:///n4/como-consulto-el-historial-de-operaciones" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">Conocé cómo consultar el historial de operaciones.</span></strong></a></p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph ghq-is-empty" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"></p>',
