    htmlContent:
      '<p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">Podrán autorizar operaciones en Office Banking y App Galicia Office todos los usuarios que cumplan los siguientes requisitos:</p><ul class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST"><li class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST_ITEM">Usuario dado de alta.</li><li class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST_ITEM">Apoderado de la cuenta.</li><li class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST_ITEM">Permisos sobre la cuenta y/o operación. <a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="http:///n4/como-edito-los-permisos-de-los-usuarios" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">Conocé cómo otorgar permisos a otros usuarios.</span></strong></a></li><li class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST_ITEM">Métodos de autenticación activo (<a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="http:///n4/como-instalo-mi-firma-digital-en-la-computadora" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Firma digital</strong></span></a> u <a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="http:///n4/como-activo-el-office-token" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Office Token</strong></span></a>).</li></ul><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph ghq-is-empty" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"></p>',
