    htmlContent:
      '<h2 class="ghq-card-content__medium-heading" data-ghq-card-content-type="MEDIUM_HEADING"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Por Office Banking</strong></h2><ol class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST" start="1"><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Ingresá a <a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="https://wsec06.bancogalicia.com.ar/pagorecurrente/ini/adhesiones" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Pagos &gt; Pago de servicios &gt;  Gestionar servicios</strong></span><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">↗</strong></span> </a></li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Clic en <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">"Nuevo servicio"</strong> y completá los datos del rubro y empresa. Necesitás el <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">código de pago o identificador </strong>que se encuentra en la boleta del servicio.</li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Hacé clic en "Agregar" y<strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"> ¡listo!</strong></li></ol><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">Conocé más sobre cómo adherir un servicio con <a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?t=1s&amp;v=IWxip4xi_Wg" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">este video.</span></strong></a></p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">☝️ Después de hacer estos pasos, vas a poder consultar las deudas de tus servicios y <a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="http:///n4/como-pago-un-servicio" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">abonarlos directamente en el calendario.</span></strong></a></p><h2 class="ghq-card-content__medium-heading" data-ghq-card-content-type="MEDIUM_HEADING"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Por App Galicia Office</strong></h2><ol class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST" start="1"><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Desde Más &gt; Pago de servicios &gt; Clic en los 3 puntos (de la esquina superior derecha) &gt; Gestionar servicios.</li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Seleccioná Nuevo servicio &gt; Completá los datos &gt; Agregar y <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">¡listo!</strong></li></ol><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph ghq-is-empty" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"></p>',
