      '<h2 class="ghq-card-content__medium-heading" data-ghq-card-content-type="MEDIUM_HEADING"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Por Office Banking</strong></h2><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">Lo podés abonar de dos formas:</p><h3 class="ghq-card-content__small-heading" data-ghq-card-content-type="SMALL_HEADING"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Antes de la fecha de vencimiento:</strong></h3><ol class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST" start="1"><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Ingresá a <a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="https://wsec06.bancogalicia.com.ar/pagorecurrente/ini/preparacion" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Pagos &gt;  Pago de servicios &gt; Pagar servicios</strong></span><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">↗</strong></span></span></a></li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Seleccioná la cuenta y el servicio ya adherido &gt; Hacé clic en el botón de pagar y<strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"> ¡listo!</strong></li></ol><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">☝️ Podés seleccionar <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">hasta 30</strong> servicios juntos.</p><h3 class="ghq-card-content__small-heading" data-ghq-card-content-type="SMALL_HEADING"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">En el día de vencimiento </strong><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">desde el </strong><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">calendario de pagos:</strong></h3><ol class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST" start="1"><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM"><a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="https://wsec06.bancogalicia.com.ar/pagorecurrente/ini" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Pagos &gt; Servicios &gt; Pago de servicios</strong></span><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">↗</strong></span></span></a></li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Seleccioná la fecha en el calendario &gt; Hacé clic en <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">"Preparar pago"</strong>.</li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Elegí la cuenta &gt; Preparar pago &gt; Confirmá los datos y el monto.</li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Autorizá el pago y <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">¡listo!</strong></li></ol><h2 class="ghq-card-content__medium-heading" data-ghq-card-content-type="MEDIUM_HEADING"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Por App Galicia Office</strong></h2><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">Desde Más &gt; Pago de servicios &gt; Seleccioná el servicio &gt; Pagar y <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">¡listo!</strong></p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">Si el servicio no está adherido a tu Office Banking, tenés que <a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="http:///n4/como-pago-un-servicio-que-no-esta-adherido-a-mi-office-banking" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">seguir estos pasos.</span></strong></a></p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph ghq-is-empty" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"></p>',
