    title: "¿Cómo pago un servicio que no está adherido a mi Office Banking?",
    url: "/n4/como-pago-un-servicio-que-no-esta-adherido-a-mi-office-banking",
    type: 0,
    level: 4,
    status: 1,
    order: 0,
    parent: "6723a131832f86e945c0300d",
    guruId: "6ae81956-9fe9-4d5a-86b6-82797b76bf49",
    htmlContent:
      '<h2 class="ghq-card-content__medium-heading" data-ghq-card-content-type="MEDIUM_HEADING"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Por Office Banking</strong></h2><ol class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST" start="1"><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Ingresá a <a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="https://wsec06.bancogalicia.com.ar/pagorecurrente/ini/nuevopago" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">Pagos &gt; Pago de servicios &gt; Nuevo pago</span></strong><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">↗</strong></span></span></a></li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Elegí el rubro, la empresa y el código de pago electrónico &gt; Continuar.</li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Confirmá la cuenta y el monto &gt; Preparar pago &gt; Ir a autorizar.</li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Ingresá el <a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="http:///n4/como-genero-un-codigo-token" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">código Office Token</span></strong></a> que se genere y tocá "Continuar".</li></ol><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">¡Listo!</strong> Una vez abonado, el servicio quedará adherido automáticamente a tu calendario de pagos donde vas a poder consultar los próximos vencimientos.</p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">☝️ Si el nuevo servicio no tiene emitida la facturación, no podrás pagarlo en ese momento. <a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="http:///n4/como-agrego-un-servicio-a-mi-calendario-de-pagos" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">Añadilo a tu calendario.</span></strong></a></p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">Conocé más sobre cómo pagar servicios con <a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?t=9s&amp;v=2yuILvJVp94" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">este video.</span></strong></a></p><h2 class="ghq-card-content__medium-heading" data-ghq-card-content-type="MEDIUM_HEADING"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Por App Galicia Office</strong></h2><ol class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST" start="1"><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Desde Más &gt; Pago de servicios &gt; Nuevo pago. </li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Buscá el rubro y empresa &gt; Ingresá el código de pago que está en la factura (solo números) &gt; Continuar.</li></ol><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph ghq-is-empty" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"></p><ul class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST"><li class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST_ITEM"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Si no tiene deuda vigente</strong>, el sistema te indicará que no podés pagarlo en este momento. Podés añadirlo a tu calendario desde Nuevo servicio &gt; Gestionar servicio.</li><li class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST_ITEM"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Si tiene deuda vigente</strong>, seleccioná la cuenta desde la que querés pagar &gt; Continuar &gt; Preparar pago &gt; Autorizá la operación desde <a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="https://wsec06.bancogalicia.com.ar/Transaction/ListPendingMultiple" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">Autorizar operaciones</span></strong><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">↗</strong></span></span></a></li></ul><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph ghq-is-empty" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"></p>',
