    htmlContent:
      '<p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">Podés activar notificaciones de tus vencimientos</p><h2 class="ghq-card-content__medium-heading" data-ghq-card-content-type="MEDIUM_HEADING"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Por App Galicia Office</strong></h2><ol class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST" start="1"><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Más &gt; Notificaciones &gt; Clic en el icono de "engranaje" <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">⚙ </strong>(margen superior derecho).</li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Activar la opción de <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">"Mensajes Globales".</strong></li></ol><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">¡Listo!</strong> Vas a recibir un aviso antes de la fecha de vencimiento del servicio.</p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph ghq-is-empty" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"><a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="http:///n4/como-agrego-un-servicio-a-mi-calendario-de-pagos" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">Conocé cómo agregar un servicio al calendario.</span></strong></a></p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph ghq-is-empty" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"></p>',
