    htmlContent:
      '<h2 class="ghq-card-content__medium-heading" data-ghq-card-content-type="MEDIUM_HEADING"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Por App Galicia Office</strong></h2><ol class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST" start="1"><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Generá tu <a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="http:///n4/como-genero-un-codigo-token" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">código Office Token</span></strong></a> desde la opción <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">"Más"</strong> &gt; <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">"Office Token".</strong></li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Ingresá los <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">6 dígitos</strong> como se muestra en la pantalla debajo &gt; clic en el botón <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">"Confirmar"</strong> para validar el código ingresado.</li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Luego podrás autorizarla desde <a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="https://wsec06.bancogalicia.com.ar/Transaction/ListPendingMultiple" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Autorizar operaciones</strong></span><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">↗</strong></a> y ¡listo!</li></ol><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">👆 Conocé el paso a paso de como <a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="http:///n4/como-autorizo-una-operacion" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">autorizar una operación.</span></strong></a></p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph ghq-is-empty" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"></p>',
