    htmlContent:
      '<h2 class="ghq-card-content__medium-heading" data-ghq-card-content-type="MEDIUM_HEADING"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Por Office Banking</strong></h2><ol class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST" start="1"><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Ingresá a Pagos &gt; Pagos de cobranza integrada</li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Clic en los tres puntos de opciones &gt; gestionar convenios &gt;<span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"> </strong></span><a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="https://wsec06.bancogalicia.com.ar/CobranzaIntegradaSPA/ini/gestionar-convenios/adherir-convenio" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Adherir convenio</strong></span><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#f7412d"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">↗</strong></span></a></li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Completá el número de convenio, ID del cliente y descripción.</li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Hacé clic en <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">"Adherir"</strong> y <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">¡listo!</strong></li></ol><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Importante:</strong> solicitá todos los datos necesarios al cobrador del servicio.</p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"><a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="http:///n4/como-realizo-el-pago-de-una-cobranza-integrada" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">Conocé cómo realizar el pago una vez realizada tu adhesión.</span></strong></a></p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph ghq-is-empty" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"></p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph ghq-is-empty" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"></p>',
