    parent: "6723a2f4832f86e945c03029",
    guruId: "b8134197-3c2f-42ce-8a9c-86434d9bf53e",
    htmlContent:
      '<h2 class="ghq-card-content__medium-heading" data-ghq-card-content-type="MEDIUM_HEADING"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Por Office Banking</strong></h2><ol class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST" start="1"><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Ingresá a Pagos &gt; Pagos de cobranza integrada &gt; <a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="https://wsec06.bancogalicia.com.ar/CobranzaIntegradaSPA/ini/nuevo-pago" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Nuevo pago</strong></span><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">↗</span></strong></a><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"></strong></span></li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Seleccioná el o los convenios y la forma de pago &gt; Confirmar.</li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Confirmá y <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">¡listo!</strong></li></ol><h2 class="ghq-card-content__medium-heading" data-ghq-card-content-type="MEDIUM_HEADING"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Por App Galicia Office</strong></h2><ol class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST" start="1"><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Ingresá a Pagos &gt; Pagos CIG.</li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Seleccioná las deuda a pagar &gt; Clic en Continuar.</li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Seleccioná la cuenta a debitar y el detalle &gt; Clic en "pagar" y <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">¡listo!</strong></li></ol><h2 class="ghq-card-content__medium-heading" data-ghq-card-content-type="MEDIUM_HEADING"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Por terminal de autoservicio</strong></h2><ol class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST" start="1"><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Ingresá a depósitos y pagos &gt; Cobranza Integrada.</li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Vas a necesitar el <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">número de convenio</strong> de la empresa y el ID del cliente.</li></ol><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">Conocé como hacerlo con <a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rMXO3TS6EvI" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">este video.</span></strong></a></p><h2 class="ghq-card-content__medium-heading" data-ghq-card-content-type="MEDIUM_HEADING"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Por BtoB</strong></h2><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">Si sos cliente Galicia, te mostramos cómo hacerlo en <a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mcxni-2ew4I" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">este video.</strong></span></a> Si no sos cliente, te recomendamos seguir el<strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"> </strong><a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jPcjdqqfLJk" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">siguiente video.</strong></span></a></p><h2 class="ghq-card-content__medium-heading" data-ghq-card-content-type="MEDIUM_HEADING"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Por caja en sucursal</strong></h2><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">Podés acercarte de lunes a viernes de <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">10 a 15 h.</strong></p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">☝️ Recordá que antes de realizar un pago por primera vez, es necesario que te adhieras al <a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="http:///n4/como-adhiero-un-servicio-de-cobranza-integrada" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">convenio.</span></strong></a></p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph ghq-is-empty" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"></p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph ghq-is-empty" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"></p>',
