    guruId: "065a8893-c55f-46da-90f5-24d8de278aa5",
    htmlContent:
      '<h3 class="ghq-card-content__small-heading" data-ghq-card-content-type="SMALL_HEADING">Paso 1</h3><ul class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST"><li class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST_ITEM">Ingresá a <a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="https://wsec06.bancogalicia.com.ar/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">Office Banking ↗</span></strong></a> con tu Nombre de Usuario y Clave de Acceso.</li><li class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST_ITEM">En el menú lateral izquierdo, seleccioná <a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="https://wsec06.bancogalicia.com.ar/Administracion/SeleccionOperadorPerfiles" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">Administrar empresas &gt; Permisos de usuarios ↗</span></strong></a>﻿</li></ul><h3 class="ghq-card-content__small-heading" data-ghq-card-content-type="SMALL_HEADING">Paso 2</h3><ul class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST"><li class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST_ITEM">En la opción <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">“Modo de asignación”</strong>, elegí <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">“Por funcionalidad”</strong> &gt; En Usuario, seleccioná el usuario que querés asignarle permisos.</li><li class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST_ITEM">Hacé clic en <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">“Continuar”.</strong></li></ul><h3 class="ghq-card-content__small-heading" data-ghq-card-content-type="SMALL_HEADING">Paso 3</h3><ul class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST"><li class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST_ITEM">Seleccioná Pagos &gt; Servicios.</li></ul><ul class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST"><li class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST_ITEM">Una vez seleccionado el producto te figurará las funcionalidades <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">"Adhesión de cobranza integrada"</strong> y <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">"Pago de cobranza integrada"</strong> &gt; Tildá en las columnas de “Consultar”, "Preparar" y si el usuario es firmante de cuenta también podés tildar "Autorizar" según el tipo de permisos que quieras otorgarle.</li></ul><ul class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST"><li class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST_ITEM">Generá el código Office Token desde tu celular con la App Galicia Office, seleccionando la opción “Office Token”.</li><li class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST_ITEM">En Office Banking ingresá el código Token en “Código de aprobación”.</li><li class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST_ITEM">Hacé clic en “Continuar”.</li></ul><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">👆 Si no tenés tu Office Token activo, te enviaremos a tu celular un SMS con un código de aprobación.</p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">¡Listo! Ya asignaste los permisos que querías.</p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph ghq-is-empty" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"></p>',
