      '<p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">Para adherir un débito automático, <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">tenés que contactarte con la empresa prestadora del servicio.</strong> Vas a ver el monto debitado automáticamente en la cuenta que elegiste, después de cada vencimiento.</p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Recordá</strong> tener a mano los datos de tu cuenta. Podrás encontrarlos:</p><h2 class="ghq-card-content__medium-heading" data-ghq-card-content-type="MEDIUM_HEADING"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Por Office Banking</strong></h2><ol class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST" start="1"><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Desde<strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60"> </span></strong><a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="https://wsec06.bancogalicia.com.ar/Miscuentasspa/ini/main" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">Inicio ↗</span></strong></a></li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Hacé clic en los 3 puntos de la cuenta que querés consultar &gt; <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">"Ver datos de cuenta".</strong></li></ol><h3 class="ghq-card-content__small-heading" data-ghq-card-content-type="SMALL_HEADING">Encontrarás:</h3><ul class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST"><li class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST_ITEM">Número de cuenta</li><li class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST_ITEM">CUIT</li><li class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST_ITEM">Razón social</li><li class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST_ITEM">CBU</li><li class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST_ITEM">Alias</li></ul><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">Importante: por planes de facilidades o moratorias de AFIP deberás realizarlo desde la página de AFIP, en la sección "Adhesiones de débitos automáticos de AFIP".</p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph ghq-is-empty" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"></p>',
