    htmlContent:
      '<h2 class="ghq-card-content__medium-heading" data-ghq-card-content-type="MEDIUM_HEADING"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Por Office Banking</strong></h2><ol class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST" start="1"><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Accedé a <a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="https://wsec06.bancogalicia.com.ar/Transferencias/NuevaTransferencia/receipts" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">Pagos &gt; Transferencias &gt; Clic en los tres puntos (arriba a la derecha)↗</span></strong></a></li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">En "Filtros" seleccioná las fechas &gt; Aplicar.</li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Selecciona la transferencia &gt; Clic en <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">"descargar comprobantes" &gt; </strong>Confimá y<span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#66a030"> </span><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">¡listo!</strong></li></ol><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#66a030">☝️ </span>Podrás hacer clic en <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">"ver detalles"</strong> para conocer todos los datos de la operación.</p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph ghq-is-empty" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"></p>',
