    guruId: "89995603-8b69-40ab-a5c3-bdb6deeaf211",
    htmlContent:
      '<p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">Si pagás por:</p><h2 class="ghq-card-content__medium-heading" data-ghq-card-content-type="MEDIUM_HEADING">Transferencias a cuentas Galicia</h2><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">Hasta las<strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"> 21 h todos los días hábiles </strong>y el pago se acreditará ese mismo día.</p><h2 class="ghq-card-content__medium-heading" data-ghq-card-content-type="MEDIUM_HEADING">A cuentas de otros bancos</h2><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">Hasta las<strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"> 17 h</strong> <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">todos los días hábiles</strong> y el pago se acreditará ese mismo día o al siguiente día hábil, según el banco destino.</p><h2 class="ghq-card-content__medium-heading" data-ghq-card-content-type="MEDIUM_HEADING">Cheques electrónicos</h2><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">Hasta las <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">21 h</strong> <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">todos los días hábiles. </strong>El pago se acreditará cuando quien recibe el cheque lo acepte y deposite.</p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">☝️ Recordá que:</p><ul class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST"><li class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST_ITEM">Debés tener saldo en tu cuenta y la autorización de los firmantes de la empresa.</li><li class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST_ITEM">Podés autorizar tus pagos<strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"> por </strong><a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="https://wsec06.bancogalicia.com.ar/Transaction/ListPendingMultiple" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">Office Banking &gt; </span></strong><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Autorizar Operaciones ↗</strong></span></a> o desde la App Galicia Office &gt; Autorizar. </li></ul><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph ghq-is-empty" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"><a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="http:///n4/como-autorizo-una-operacion" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">Conocé cómo autorizar tus operaciones</span></strong></a></p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph ghq-is-empty" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"></p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph ghq-is-empty" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"></p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph ghq-is-empty" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"></p>',
