    title: "¿Cómo otorgo o modifico permisos para Pagos?",
    url: "/n4/como-otorgo-o-modifico-permisos-pagos",
    type: 0,
    level: 4,
    status: 1,
    order: 0,
    parent: "67239ef3832f86e945c02ff8",
    guruId: "20bed592-cbd8-4d79-ad49-06a841060db5",
    htmlContent:
      '<p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">Para que vos u otros usuarios puedan usar todas las funcionalidades de pagos, deberás habilitar los permisos necesarios. Podés hacerlo:</p><h2 class="ghq-card-content__medium-heading" data-ghq-card-content-type="MEDIUM_HEADING"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Por Office Banking</strong></h2><h3 class="ghq-card-content__small-heading" data-ghq-card-content-type="SMALL_HEADING">Paso 1</h3><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">• Ingresá a <a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="https://wsec06.bancogalicia.com.ar/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">Office Banking ↗</span></strong></a> con tu Nombre de Usuario y Clave de Acceso.</p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">• En el menú lateral izquierdo, seleccioná <a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="https://wsec06.bancogalicia.com.ar/Administracion/SeleccionOperadorPerfiles" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">Administrar empresas &gt; Permisos de usuarios ↗</span></strong></a></p><h3 class="ghq-card-content__small-heading" data-ghq-card-content-type="SMALL_HEADING">Paso 2</h3><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">• En la opción <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">“Modo de asignación”</strong>, elegí <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">“Por funcionalidad”</strong> &gt; En Usuario, seleccioná el usuario que querés asignarle permisos. </p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">• Hacé clic en <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">“Continuar”.</strong></p><h3 class="ghq-card-content__small-heading" data-ghq-card-content-type="SMALL_HEADING">Paso 3</h3><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">• Seleccioná <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Pagos</strong> &gt; Luego seleccioná el producto que quieras dar permisos al usuario:</p><ul class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST"><li class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST_ITEM"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Haberes</strong></li><li class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST_ITEM"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Pagos DEBIN</strong></li><li class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST_ITEM"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Pagos Masivos</strong></li><li class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST_ITEM"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Transferencias y Pagos</strong></li><li class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST_ITEM"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Servicios</strong></li><li class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST_ITEM"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">AFIP</strong></li><li class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST_ITEM"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Débito automático en cuenta</strong></li><li class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST_ITEM"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Fondos de Cese Laboral</strong></li></ul><h3 class="ghq-card-content__small-heading" data-ghq-card-content-type="SMALL_HEADING">Paso 4</h3><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">• Una vez seleccionado el producto te figurará el/la funcionalidad/es que podés otorgar al usuario &gt; Tildá en las columnas de <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">“Consultar”</strong>, <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">"Preparar"</strong> y si el usuario es firmante de cuenta también podés tildar <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">"Autorizar"</strong> según el tipo de permisos que quieras otorgarle.</p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">• Generá el código Office Token desde tu celular con la App Galicia Office, seleccionando la opción <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">“Office Token”.</strong></p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">• En Office Banking ingresá el código Token en <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">“Código de aprobación”.</strong></p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">• Hacé clic en <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">“Continuar”.</strong></p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">👆 Si no tenés tu Office Token activo, te enviaremos a tu celular un <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">SMS</strong> con un código de aprobación.</p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">¡Listo!</strong> Ya asignaste los permisos que querías.</p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph ghq-is-empty" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"></p>',
