    guruId: "0c6731cf-1919-42bd-bd52-1487b5221eeb",
    htmlContent:
      '<p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">El endoso es transferir el derecho de cobrar el dinero a un nuevo beneficiario. Las condiciones del cheque, el monto y la fecha de pago <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">no cambian</strong>.</p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">Para transferir un cheque tiene que ser<strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60"> </span></strong><a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="http:///n4/que-tipos-de-cheques-existen" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">a la orden</span></strong></a> y tenés que endosarlo.</p><h3 class="ghq-card-content__small-heading" data-ghq-card-content-type="SMALL_HEADING"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Para endosar un cheque</strong></h3><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">En la parte de atrás, tenés que indicar la frase "<strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">pagar a la orden de</strong>". Tendrás que firmar y completar los datos de la persona que cobrará el cheque:</p><ul class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST"><li class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST_ITEM">Nombre completo o CUIT</li><li class="ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="BULLETED_LIST_ITEM">Dirección y teléfono</li></ul><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph ghq-is-empty" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"></p>',
