    guruId: "10fadd33-2452-4b65-8927-62602a0ba96f",
    htmlContent:
      '<p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">Si sos beneficiario, podés aceptar o repudiar el cheque recibido.</p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">Una vez que lo aceptes, el cheque estará en tu poder y podrás cobrarlo, endosarlo o cederlo, según corresponda. Si no estás de acuerdo con las condiciones del cheque, podés repudiar y volverá a la persona que lo envió. Podés hacerlo: </p><h2 class="ghq-card-content__medium-heading" data-ghq-card-content-type="MEDIUM_HEADING"><br><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Por Office Banking</strong></h2><ol class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST" start="1"><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Desde <a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="https://wsec06.bancogalicia.com.ar/ChequeElectronicoReact/Overview/recibidos" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><u class="ghq-card-content__underline" data-ghq-card-content-type="UNDERLINE" style="text-decoration:underline"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">Cuentas &gt; Cheques &gt; Recibidos </span></strong></u><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">↗</span></strong></a></li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Hacé clic en Aceptar &gt; Seleccioná el o los cheques que querés (<strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">hasta 20</strong>).</li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Elegí entre "Repudiar" o "Aceptar".</li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Aceptá los términos y condiciones e ingresá el motivo, en caso de repudio.</li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Confirmá y <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">¡listo!</strong></li></ol><h2 class="ghq-card-content__medium-heading" data-ghq-card-content-type="MEDIUM_HEADING"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Por App Galicia Office</strong></h2><ol class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST" start="1"><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Desde Más &gt; Cheques electrónicos &gt; Recibidos.</li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Hacé clic en Aceptar &gt; Seleccioná el o los cheques que querés (<strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">hasta 20</strong>).</li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Elegí entre "Repudiar" o "Aceptar".</li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Aceptá los términos y condiciones e ingresá el motivo, en caso de repudio.</li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Confirmá y <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">¡listo!</strong></li></ol><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">☝️ Si aceptaste, lo vas a encontrar en estado "<strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Disponible"</strong> y si repudiaste, volverá a la persona que libró el cheque.<br></p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph ghq-is-empty" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"></p>',
