      '<h2 class="ghq-card-content__medium-heading" data-ghq-card-content-type="MEDIUM_HEADING"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Por Office Banking</strong></h2><ol class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST" start="1"><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Ingresá a <a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="https://wsec06.bancogalicia.com.ar/ChequeElectronicoReact/Overview" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><u class="ghq-card-content__underline" data-ghq-card-content-type="UNDERLINE" style="text-decoration:underline"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">Cuentas &gt; Cheques↗</span></strong></u></a> &gt; Emitidos y/o recibidos (dependiendo de lo que quieras consultar).</li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Hacé clic en los 3 puntos a la derecha del cheque que querés descargar el detalle &gt; Seleccioná Ver detalle.</li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Hacé clic en Descargar detalle y<strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"> ¡listo!</strong></li></ol><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">☝️ Recordá que es <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">solo un detalle</strong> de tu operación.</p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph ghq-is-empty" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"></p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph ghq-is-empty" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"></p>',
