    htmlContent:
      '<h2 class="ghq-card-content__medium-heading" data-ghq-card-content-type="MEDIUM_HEADING"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Por Office Banking</strong></h2><ol class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST" start="1"><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Ingresá a <a class="ghq-card-content__link" data-ghq-card-content-type="LINK" href="https://wsec06.bancogalicia.com.ar/ChequeElectronicoReact/Overview/recibidos/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><u class="ghq-card-content__underline" data-ghq-card-content-type="UNDERLINE" style="text-decoration:underline"><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD"><span class="ghq-card-content__text-color" data-ghq-card-content-type="TEXT_COLOR" style="color:#ff8a60">Cuentas &gt; Cheques &gt; Recibidos↗</span></strong></u></a> &gt; Consultar.</li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Seleccioná los 3 puntos del cheque que querés &gt; Solicitar aval.</li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Ingresá el CUIT, domicilio del avalista y motivo del aval &gt; Continuar.</li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Aceptá los términos y condiciones.</li><li class="ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item" data-ghq-card-content-type="NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM">Confirmá la solicitud de aval y <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">¡listo!</strong></li></ol><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph">☝️ Quedará en estado <strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">"</strong><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">Aval pendiente</strong><strong class="ghq-card-content__bold" data-ghq-card-content-type="BOLD">"</strong> hasta que el avalista acepte o rechace el aval, podrás consultarlo haciendo clic en el cheque e ingresando al detalle de Avales.<br></p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph ghq-is-empty" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"></p><p class="ghq-card-content__paragraph ghq-is-empty" data-ghq-card-content-type="paragraph"></p>',
